Video Player is quite easy to install.

1. Untar the extension in your extensions/ directory, and activate it using the
   admin interface or by editing override/site.ini.append.php.
2. Import the "flash_video" package from the doc/ directory.
3. Add the contents of doc/override.ini.append to the override.ini.append.php
   files in your siteaccesses.
4. Clear your caches.
